Helm = Package Manager for Kubernetes
Helm manages Kubernetes applications
Instead of writing many YAML files manually (deployment + service + ingress…),
Helm packages everything into one unit → Chart


nginx-chart/
│
├── Chart.yaml
├── values.yaml
├── charts/
└── templates/
      ├── deployment.yaml
      ├── service.yaml
      ├── ingress.yaml
      └── hpa.yaml



---
helm install myapp ./chart
helm install my-nginx ./nginx-chart